---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="ShopStack Online" description="A complete online business stack for sellers and digital creators — storefront, email, file storage, and invoicing. No platform fees. No per-user charges. $99/mo flat.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">ShopStack Online</div>
      <h1>Your store. Your email.<br/>No platform fees eating your margin.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        A complete managed stack for online sellers and digital creators — storefront,
        professional email, file storage, and invoicing. You own the infrastructure.
        Woodhead Tech runs it.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Setup Call →</a>
        <a href="#pricing" class="btn btn-ghost">See pricing</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-for">Built for: Etsy sellers &nbsp;·&nbsp; digital product shops &nbsp;·&nbsp; online boutiques &nbsp;·&nbsp; independent creators</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain -->
  <section class="section pain-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Platform fees add up fast.</h2>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="pain-card card">
          <div class="pain-num">6.5%</div>
          <p>Etsy's transaction fee on every sale — on top of listing fees, payment processing, and offsite ads. That's before you pay yourself.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card card">
          <div class="pain-num">$66+</div>
          <p>What most online sellers pay monthly just to have Shopify Basic, a Google email, and somewhere to store product files. Plus transaction fees on every order.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card card">
          <div class="pain-num">0%</div>
          <p>Platform transaction fees on ShopStack Online. Stripe's standard 2.9% + 30¢ per transaction — that's it. No additional cut to a platform that doesn't know your name.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What you get -->
  <section class="section" id="stack">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">The Stack</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything you need to run an online business.</h2>
      <p class="stack-sub">
        ShopStack Online is the same battle-tested open-source infrastructure used by
        serious online businesses — right-sized and managed so you can focus on selling,
        not on servers.
      </p>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-item card">
          <div class="service-icon">🛒</div>
          <div class="service-name">WooCommerce Storefront</div>
          <div class="service-desc">A full e-commerce store at your own domain. Product pages, cart, checkout, order management — no Etsy listing fees, no platform transaction cut.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item card">
          <div class="service-icon">📬</div>
          <div class="service-name">Business Email</div>
          <div class="service-desc">Professional email at @yourdomain.com. Works with any email client. No Google Workspace. No per-user fees. Looks like a real business — because you are one.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item card">
          <div class="service-icon">📦</div>
          <div class="service-name">Digital Product Delivery</div>
          <div class="service-desc">Nextcloud handles your digital files — send secure download links to customers after purchase. No third-party delivery platform skimming a cut.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item card">
          <div class="service-icon">💳</div>
          <div class="service-name">Invoicing &amp; Payments</div>
          <div class="service-desc">Send professional invoices and collect Stripe payments. Automatic invoices on order. Client portal included. No platform fees — just Stripe's standard rate.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item card">
          <div class="service-icon">📁</div>
          <div class="service-name">File Storage</div>
          <div class="service-desc">Shared cloud storage for your product files, design assets, and business documents — separate from your personal life. Access from anywhere.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item card">
          <div class="service-icon">📡</div>
          <div class="service-name">Uptime Monitoring</div>
          <div class="service-desc">Woodhead Tech gets paged the moment anything goes wrong. Most issues are resolved before your customers notice. You don't have to watch it.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hosting-note card">
        <div class="hosting-icon">☁️</div>
        <div class="hosting-text">
          <div class="hosting-title">Cloud-hosted. No hardware required.</div>
          <div class="hosting-desc">ShopStack Online runs on managed cloud infrastructure — AWS or GCP. No box to plug in. No hardware to buy. Accessible from anywhere. Live in under 48 hours after onboarding.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="section pricing-section" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">Pricing</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">One flat rate. No surprises.</h2>

      <div class="pricing-wrapper">
        <div class="price-card card featured-card">
          <div class="price-badge">ShopStack Online</div>
          <div class="price-main">
            <span class="price-setup">$99</span>
            <span class="price-setup-label">setup &nbsp;+&nbsp;</span>
            <span class="price-mo">$99<span class="price-per">/mo</span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="price-annual">$1,287 first year · $1,188/yr after</div>

          <ul class="includes-list">
            <li><strong>WooCommerce storefront at your domain</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Professional email at @yourdomain.com</strong></li>
            <li>Digital product delivery via Nextcloud</li>
            <li>Invoicing + Stripe payments (Invoice Ninja)</li>
            <li>Cloud file storage</li>
            <li>Domain + DNS configuration</li>
            <li>Monthly OS &amp; software patching</li>
            <li>24/7 uptime monitoring (we get paged, not you)</li>
            <li>Up to 1 hr support included each month</li>
            <li>Rolling month-to-month — cancel anytime</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary cta-btn">Get Started →</a>
          <div class="price-note">No AWS/GCP account needed · Live in under 48 hours · Additional support at $150/hr</div>
        </div>

        <div class="compare-box card">
          <div class="compare-title">What you'd pay otherwise</div>
          <div class="compare-rows">
            <div class="compare-row">
              <span class="compare-item">Shopify Basic</span>
              <span class="compare-price">$39/mo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="compare-row">
              <span class="compare-item">Google Workspace</span>
              <span class="compare-price">$12/user/mo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="compare-row">
              <span class="compare-item">Dropbox</span>
              <span class="compare-price">$15/mo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="compare-row">
              <span class="compare-item">Shopify transaction fee</span>
              <span class="compare-price">1–2% per sale</span>
            </div>
            <div class="compare-row compare-total">
              <span class="compare-item">Total</span>
              <span class="compare-price">$66+/mo + fees</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="compare-vs">
            <div class="compare-vs-label">ShopStack Online</div>
            <div class="compare-vs-price">$99/mo flat</div>
            <div class="compare-vs-note">No transaction fees. No per-user charges. No platform taking a cut of your sales.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <section class="section how-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">How it works</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">From zero to live in 48 hours.</h2>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card card">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <div class="step-title">Book a setup call</div>
          <div class="step-desc">30 minutes. Woodhead Tech asks about your domain, your products, and what you're migrating from. You ask anything you want.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card card">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <div class="step-title">Woodhead Tech builds it</div>
          <div class="step-desc">Storefront, email, storage, invoicing — all provisioned and configured. You don't touch a server. You don't need an AWS account.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card card">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <div class="step-title">You start selling</div>
          <div class="step-desc">You get logins to everything. Woodhead Tech handles updates, monitoring, and support. You focus on your business.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I migrate my existing Etsy or Shopify store?</h3>
          <p>Yes. The setup call covers what you're migrating from. Product data, images, and customer records can be imported. Existing orders stay in their original platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do I need any technical knowledge?</h3>
          <p>No. You'll get a WooCommerce admin login — adding products, managing orders, and running promotions works the same as any other store builder. Woodhead Tech handles everything underneath.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What about payment processing?</h3>
          <p>ShopStack Online uses Stripe — 2.9% + 30¢ per transaction, the same rate you'd pay anywhere. No additional platform fee on top. Your sales stay your sales.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can I sell digital products?</h3>
          <p>Yes. Nextcloud handles secure file delivery — customers get a download link after purchase. No third-party digital delivery platform needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What if I want to cancel?</h3>
          <p>Month-to-month, cancel anytime. You own your domain and your data. Woodhead Tech will export everything so you can move it wherever you want.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How is this different from regular ShopStack?</h3>
          <p>Regular ShopStack is built for brick-and-mortar businesses — vet clinics, salons, retail shops — that need local hardware and offline capability. ShopStack Online is for businesses that operate entirely online. Different ICP, different stack, same managed approach.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <h2>Ready to stop paying Etsy and Shopify for the privilege of running your own business?</h2>
        <p>Book a 30-minute setup call. Woodhead Tech will walk through what you have now and what the migration looks like. No pressure, no pitch — just a real conversation.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Setup Call →</a>
        <div class="cta-also">
          Also looking for managed infrastructure for a physical business?
          <a href="/shopstack">See ShopStack for brick-and-mortar →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-for {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* Pain */
  .pain-section { background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .pain-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

  .pain-num {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .pain-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* Stack */
  .stack-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 620px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }

  .service-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; }

  .service-name {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .service-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  .hosting-note {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hosting-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .hosting-title {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .hosting-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Pricing */
  .pricing-section { background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .pricing-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
    max-width: 880px;
  }

  .price-card { padding: 2rem; }

  .featured-card {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent), 0 8px 32px rgba(232, 88, 12, 0.08);
  }

  .price-badge {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .price-main {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .price-setup {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .price-setup-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .price-mo {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .price-per { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--muted); }

  .price-annual {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .includes-list li {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .includes-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .cta-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .price-note { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Comparison box */
  .compare-box { padding: 1.75rem; }

  .compare-title {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .compare-rows { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .compare-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .compare-total {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .compare-vs {
    background: rgba(232, 88, 12, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(232, 88, 12, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .compare-vs-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .compare-vs-price {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .compare-vs-note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* How it works */
  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .step-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .step-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }

  .step-desc { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-section { background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-item h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .faq-item p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .cta-box {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 1.9rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .cta-box p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

  .cta-also {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .cta-also a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; margin-left: 0.25rem; }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .pain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .pricing-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero { padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
  }
</style>
